From: Herbert Xu <herbert@gondor.apana.org.au>
Subject: Fix potential DoS in load_elf_library
Patch-mainline: no
References: 73837

Yichen Xie <yxie@cs.stanford.edu> points out that load_elf_library can
modify `elf_phdata' before freeing it.

Signed-off-by: Andrew Morton <akpm@osdl.org>
Acked-by: mason@suse.de

diff -urNp linux-2.6.11/fs/binfmt_elf.c linux-2.6.11.SUSE/fs/binfmt_elf.c
--- linux-2.6.11/fs/binfmt_elf.c	2005-03-02 08:38:08.000000000 +0100
+++ linux-2.6.11.SUSE/fs/binfmt_elf.c	2005-04-01 12:19:21.687177055 +0200
@@ -1008,6 +1008,7 @@ out_free_ph:
